name: Lamington Ice-Cream Scones Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Halve lamingtons and spread cut side with chocolate hazelnut spread.
Using a fork, lightly break up raspberries in a small bowl. Distribute raspberries amongst half the lamington halves.
Top each raspberry lamington half with a scoop of ice-cream, then sandwich with remaining lamington halves. Serve immediately.
